room_title: Escape room "R.E.S.C.U.E." by Denver Escape Room in Denver
room_address: 11674 N Huron St, Suite 300, Northglenn, Colorado 80234
room_description: A young girl has gone missing and a tactical response team has been formed to find her. In the hunt to track down the kidnappers, your team discovers an abandoned warehouse. You must search the building and find anything that could lead to her rescue. Threats of a bomb are found and time is running out.
